stories.title: Ponting salutes Dutch courage
stories.summary: Australia's captain Ricky Ponting had warm praise for the Netherlands after his side clinched a comfortable 75-run win in their rain-affected World Cup Pool A clash in Potchefstroom.

stories.title: Potchefstroom ground staff help Australia to four points
stories.summary: A sterling effort by the groundsmen, administrators and a willing Netherlands team saw Australia run out winners in a rain-affected match at the North West Stadium in Potchefstroom.
